entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="jpn" o="連中は何か企んでる。こっちも手を打っておかねえと" t="Heard they're planning something big. Gotta make sure we're prepped." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="私に3人ほどつけてよ。こっちから仕掛けてやる" t="Give me three people. I'll handle it – they won't know what hit 'em." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="今4人も失うリスクは負えねえよ。普段ならお前がどこで死のうが知ったこっちゃねえがな" t="Believe me, I'd love to get rid of four gonks. But sadly, that's a luxury I can't afford." b="" a=""/>
